Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:07.98,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片轻描淡写地讲述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.35,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  6  7  8  9…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝天椒要切成丝放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多炒会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了  速水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂你想继续做料理到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人只要活着就少不了吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做料理之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是死亡之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是可以考虑偶尔用些其它方法来引春香注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说  你看  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10  11  12  13  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14  15  16  17…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是16
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这个越来越冷的季节是必不可少的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始努力说不定能赶在圣诞节之前送出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提从今年的流行和我的喜好上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐这种感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  加油试试看吧  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒假到来之前完成它…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了南春香开始做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术上的确进步了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还没有让她笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前连话都没有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不成熟的双手不论做什么都不成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来我令南春香展开笑容的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时再开始织东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让她和女儿们得到温暖的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香说过喜欢织的东西哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么从今天开始我也喜欢织东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31  诶？  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32  33  34  35  36  37…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在编织的时候最重要的是平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦躁了会织错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力过大会网眼会缠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适当休息下  做些伸展运动之类的悠闲地织吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之享受才是织东西的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？网眼多了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个网眼用力不均宽度就会变吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真深奥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,55  56  57  58…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的圣诞节可以期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:42.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}圣夜、神仙下凡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希穿了新大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为变冷了  不过今天更冷了一个级别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  特别冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子的围巾毛绒绒的感觉很厚很暖和  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个很暖和所以很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希的大衣感觉也很暖和真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是新买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希问问题的意图很容易懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子能理解我问题的意图真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有点烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  想问你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味的牛奶可可和加了过多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得哪个更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可？咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为选哪个而烦恼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在打比方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味牛奶可可和放了过多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道淡加点就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一边只要再加些咖啡就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还要加热水和糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把放多了的味道调回去会很难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可可更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吗  淳子也这样想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真希今天早上穿的大衣是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「淡味的牛奶可可」色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个都是不对的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了保坂学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  你怎样想？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个到底是重复了呢还是没重复呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白意图的二选一问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会不会选哪个都是不对的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个重复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有重复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能两个都不是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得真希新大衣的颜色和南春香大衣的颜色重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本身并不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上说答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是少见的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复了也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拿铁咖啡的颜色进入到视线的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会困惑也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可去的心情该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无计可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为什么  无处可去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些问题似乎多想无用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时里说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的价值是由被男生告白的次数决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说那句话的是竞争对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那之后被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管这样我觉得还是有一番道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何内田  最近很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:43.07,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也无济于事的话还是不要去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我怎样才能受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  淳子  老实说你很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？果然很受欢迎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是有受欢迎秘诀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样才能受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样才能受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我什么都没有想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂内田  什么都不想就会受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？夏奈那种事情可能吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来淳子是被称为魔女的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定拥有魔法之类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的魔法使？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一个说害羞的话也不脸红的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事情  淳子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我受欢迎的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我恋爱的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上皇家奶茶色的大衣之类的会好一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  有皇家奶茶色的大衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  借我皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.92,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我什么脑筋都没动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.60,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好嘛拜托了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给你用的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么啊千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上了春香的皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就受欢迎了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把别人认成了南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空也在嘲笑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到下的这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓纯白就是那样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  掀开窗帘就是满面的银色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒来的时候窗帘已经被妹妹拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经相当的兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跳出窗外被雪埋上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹已经这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也像她那么年轻也会跳出去被雪埋上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话真想雪再积得深一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就可以堆雪屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温馨的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会下雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.8度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  哪里不舒服么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力  量了体温
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只是低烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐也来量体温？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然变冷了  很怕感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的雪也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我先离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…还是扣上比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才量体温之后忘记扣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用这种坚定又纯真的少年的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  简直就是满面的纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别特地把颜色说出来啊  纯白什么的别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为打开着一下子就充满了视野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是故意的…什么  兴…兴奋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来软绵绵地非常柔软  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞扑上去一定很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞…飞扑什么的  就在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再年轻一些就会扑上去深埋进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有多大啊  不是跟我同岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来还真可惜  能再大一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你也看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.5也算正常体温吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是有些乏力  不过加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我说  夏树看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…还是说快要看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是白茫茫的一片呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的纯白色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也没在看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明积了这么多雪  是没在看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  在生什么气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为别的  都是因为夏树那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个差劲的男人  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不揍他一顿就咽不下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口被那家伙看了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是目不转睛的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…刚才…夏树他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还用少年纯真的眼神说什么纯白很漂亮什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说他很兴奋什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说看起来软绵绵很柔软的样子  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飞扑上去什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飞扑上去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还说要是再年轻一些就危险了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说我已经老了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还说要是再大一点就好了  太差劲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
